Movie Info

On a college campus, a rash of unexplained bizarre deaths has left victims all literally frozen to death. A shy college freshman starts to suspect that two hottest blondes on campus are somehow behind it and that they are aliens. However, nobody believes him, and it is up to him to save his friends.


Decoys: The Second Seduction


Sam, a college student in a small Northwestern town, reluctantly joins his roommates in a contest to see who can hook up with the most gorgeous co-eds by the end of the semester. But when men slowly start disappearing around town, he and his friends learn that when it comes to beautiful women, it's what's inside that really matters.
